postReview.title: Tottenham 1-2 Newcastle United: Ramsey winner piles more pressure on Frank
postReview.description: Tottenham's relegation fears were deepened by a 2-1 defeat to Newcastle United, who bounced back after three straight Premier League losses.

postReview.title: Tottenham 1-2 Newcastle United: El gol de Ramsey aumenta la presión sobre Frank
postReview.description: El temor al descenso del Tottenham se agravó con una derrota por 2-1 ante el Newcastle United, que reaccionó tras tres derrotas seguidas en la Premier League.
